{"id":353,"date":"2026-03-05T05:12:32","date_gmt":"2026-03-05T05:12:32","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/?p=353"},"modified":"2026-03-13T02:42:58","modified_gmt":"2026-03-13T02:42:58","slug":"actions-pour-une-reappropriation-politique-de-la-notion-de-ville-inclusive","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/?p=353","title":{"rendered":"Actions pour une r\u00e9appropriation politique de la notion de \u00ab ville inclusive \u00bb"},"content":{"rendered":"\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. Assembl\u00e9es populaires de quartier<\/h1>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Action<\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Organiser des <strong>assembl\u00e9es populaires de quartier<\/strong> pour red\u00e9finir collectivement ce que signifie \u00ab inclusion \u00bb.<!--more--><\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Concr\u00e8tement<\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\r\n<li>r\u00e9unions publiques dans les quartiers populaires<\/li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>prise de parole libre des habitants<\/li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>r\u00e9daction collective d\u2019un <strong>\u201cManifeste de la ville r\u00e9ellement inclusive\u201d<\/strong><\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Objectif<\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>D\u00e9placer la d\u00e9finition de l\u2019inclusion :<br \/>pas seulement <strong>accessibilit\u00e9 physique<\/strong>, mais aussi<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\r\n<li>acc\u00e8s aux d\u00e9cisions<\/li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>acc\u00e8s aux ressources urbaines<\/li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>\u00e9galit\u00e9 territoriale.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" \/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. Audit citoyen de l\u2019inclusion municipale<\/h1>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Action<\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Cr\u00e9er un <strong>observatoire citoyen de l\u2019inclusion dans la ville<\/strong>.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Concr\u00e8tement<\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Un groupe d\u2019habitants analyse :<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\r\n<li>r\u00e9partition des \u00e9quipements publics<\/li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>acc\u00e8s aux transports<\/li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>politiques de logement<\/li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>repr\u00e9sentativit\u00e9 dans les instances municipales.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">R\u00e9sultat<\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Publier chaque ann\u00e9e un <strong>\u201cbarom\u00e8tre de l\u2019inclusion r\u00e9elle\u201d<\/strong>.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Objectif : montrer l\u2019\u00e9cart entre <strong>discours municipal<\/strong> et <strong>r\u00e9alit\u00e9 sociale<\/strong>.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" \/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3. Budget participatif orient\u00e9 quartiers populaires<\/h1>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Action<\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Exiger qu\u2019au moins <strong>30 \u00e0 40 % du budget participatif municipal<\/strong> soit r\u00e9serv\u00e9 aux quartiers populaires.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Pourquoi<\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Les budgets participatifs existants b\u00e9n\u00e9ficient souvent aux quartiers d\u00e9j\u00e0 organis\u00e9s socialement.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Effet<\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Donner un <strong>pouvoir concret d\u2019investissement aux habitants<\/strong>.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" \/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">4. Conseils citoyens d\u00e9cisionnels<\/h1>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Action<\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Transformer les conseils citoyens consultatifs en <strong>instances d\u00e9cisionnelles locales<\/strong>.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Concr\u00e8tement<\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\r\n<li>pouvoir de veto sur certains projets urbains<\/li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>participation aux commissions municipales<\/li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>pr\u00e9sence d\u2019habitants tir\u00e9s au sort.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Objectif<\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Sortir les habitants du r\u00f4le de <strong>public consult\u00e9<\/strong>.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" \/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">5. Campagne visuelle dans l\u2019espace public<\/h1>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Utiliser votre visuel pour une <strong>campagne d\u2019affichage militant<\/strong>.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Slogan possible<\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\u201cVille inclusive ? Alors partageons le pouvoir.\u201d<\/strong><\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Supports<\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\r\n<li>affiches A2 dans les quartiers<\/li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>r\u00e9seaux sociaux<\/li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>autocollants militants<\/li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>projections murales lors d\u2019\u00e9v\u00e9nements.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" \/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">6. Marche annuelle pour la ville r\u00e9ellement inclusive<\/h1>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Action<\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Organiser une <strong>marche urbaine militante<\/strong>.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Parcours symbolique<\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\r\n<li>d\u00e9part : quartier populaire<\/li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>passage devant \u00e9quipements publics ferm\u00e9s ou inaccessibles<\/li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>arriv\u00e9e : mairie.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Objectif<\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Montrer <strong>la g\u00e9ographie r\u00e9elle de l\u2019exclusion urbaine<\/strong>.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" \/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">7. Universit\u00e9 populaire de la ville<\/h1>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Action<\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Mettre en place une <strong>formation citoyenne ouverte<\/strong> sur :<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\r\n<li>discriminations urbaines<\/li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>racisme structurel<\/li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>politiques municipales<\/li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>droit \u00e0 la ville.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Concept inspir\u00e9 des travaux sur <strong>le droit \u00e0 la ville<\/strong> et les luttes urbaines.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" \/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">8. Pacte municipal pour l\u2019\u00e9galit\u00e9 territoriale<\/h1>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Proposition politique concr\u00e8te \u00e0 imposer dans le d\u00e9bat municipal :<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\r\n<li>r\u00e9\u00e9quilibrage des investissements entre quartiers<\/li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>priorit\u00e9 aux services publics dans les quartiers populaires<\/li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>transparence budg\u00e9taire par territoire.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" \/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">9. Strat\u00e9gie m\u00e9diatique<\/h1>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Transformer votre texte en :<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\r\n<li>tribune dans la presse locale<\/li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>vid\u00e9o courte militante<\/li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>chronique sur les r\u00e9seaux.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Objectif : <strong>d\u00e9sacraliser le discours municipal consensuel<\/strong>.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" \/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">10. Action symbolique forte<\/h1>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Une id\u00e9e qui fonctionne tr\u00e8s bien :<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Installer une <strong>\u201cfausse rampe d\u2019acc\u00e8s politique\u201d<\/strong> devant la mairie.<\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Panneau :<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\u201cRampe pour acc\u00e9der \u00e0 la mairie.<br \/>Mais o\u00f9 est la rampe pour acc\u00e9der au pouvoir ?\u201d<\/strong><\/p>\r\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>1. Assembl\u00e9es populaires de quartier Action Organiser des assembl\u00e9es populaires de quartier pour red\u00e9finir collectivement ce que signifie \u00ab inclusion<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":354,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"colormag_page_container_layout":"default_layout","colormag_page_sidebar_layout":"default_layout","footnotes":""},"categories":[33],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-353","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-le-quotidien-le-vrai"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/353","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fcomments&post=353"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/353\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":459,"href":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/353\/revisions\/459"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/media\/354"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/vesemt.org\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fmedia&parent=353"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/vesemt